      "content": "but that’s the thing, there are no small victories. it’s not just a bad patch, it’s like my whole life is designed to fail. every \"small action\" just leads right back to the start of the wheel. it's exhausting to keep trying to fix something that's just broken at the core. it feels like there's no way to actually break the cycle, just a way to keep spinning in it forever.",
